cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR 

This paper deals with computer vision and robotics, specifically with the task of depth completion using convolutional neural networks. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition). The paper also involves machine learning techniques, which makes cs.LG (Machine Learning) another likely category. The use of contextual cues and fusion of modalities suggests that the paper could also be categorized under cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The task of depth completion is relevant to robotics, which makes cs.RO (Robotics) another possible category. Finally, the paper involves image processing, which could fall under cs.GR (Graphics).
